txt.en:
By the prophecy of Lady Abrazaphel, Sauron shall be reborn by the hands of Men. As we bore witness to his downfall, we are now called to serve him once more! It is the Lady's will that his artifacts be gathered to Barad-dûr that we might prepare for his return. The Great Rings he once held in Barad-dûr may have come to rest on the shattered plains of Dor Amarth. They must be reclaimed before the fires of Orodruin consume them!
Those who deliver them to Barad-dûr shall be made deathless when at last Sauron returns!

High-priestess Khokali
